  "text": "ML1::LFY:GFP was created by ligating the 5′ portion of ML1::LFY 5′ up to the HindIII site from pAS104 [CITATION_1] and the 3′ portion of LFY:GFP from pBS-ML1::LFY-link-sGFP into the binary vector pJIHOON212 (J. H. Ahn, personal communication). 35S::LFY:GFP was created by ligating the 5′ portion of LFY cDNA from pAS107 (up to the HindIII site) with the 3′ portion of LFY:GFP into pCHF3.",
